## Configuration examples

### Minimal production values

```yaml
database:
  host: "pg.example.com"
  existingSecret: "pg-secret"
  sslMode: "require"

config:
  existingSecret: "agentregistry-secrets"

resources:
  requests:
    cpu: 250m
    memory: 256Mi
  limits:
    cpu: 500m
    memory: 512Mi
```

### Single secret for all credentials

```yaml
global:
  existingSecret: "agentregistry-all-secrets"

database:
  host: "pg.example.com"
  sslMode: "require"
```

### Namespace-scoped RBAC

```yaml
rbac:
  watchedNamespaces:
    - first-app-ns
    - second-app-ns
```

